Package jetbrains.mps.plugins.projectplugins

Class ProjectPluginManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.mps.plugins.BasePluginManager<BaseProjectPlugin>
      • jetbrains.mps.plugins.projectplugins.ProjectPluginManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.intellij.openapi.components.BaseComponent, com.intellij.openapi.components.NamedComponent, com.intellij.openapi.components.PersistentStateComponent<ProjectPluginManager.PluginsState>, com.intellij.openapi.components.ProjectComponent, PluginLoader
    public class ProjectPluginManager
extends BasePluginManager<BaseProjectPlugin>
implements com.intellij.openapi.components.ProjectComponent, com.intellij.openapi.components.PersistentStateComponent<ProjectPluginManager.PluginsState>
    Is a BasePluginManager which is responsible for loading project plugins BaseProjectPlugin; Starts listening to the reload events of PluginReloadingListener on projectOpened(). The plugin creation/disposal is triggered from the superclass (#afterPluginsCreated).
